name: This is a Farm
description: This token is a satirical take on the trend of so-called “farmers” — projects that launch coins purely to extract liquidity from users with little to no real utility. Unlike typical farmer tokens, this project is fully transparent about its purpose as a parody and social commentary. Importantly, 100% of the creator fees are directed to charity, not personal profit, aligning with a mission to turn crypto hype into real-world good.
